data.text:
Jessica Taylor is an English singer. She is best known as member of the pop group Liberty X, along with Series 15 contestant Michelle Heaton. They were the loosing band of the reality television music competition Popstars; Series 3 winner Suzanne Shaw and Series 13 contestant Myleene Klass were part of the winning group.

Jessica was a contestant in Series 4, partnering Czech skater Pavel Aubrecht and finished in third place behind the eventual winner Ray Quinn and runner up Donal MacIntyre. She had previously found herself in the save me skate in weeks 7 and 9, eliminating television presenters Melinda Messenger and Zoe Salmon respectively.
